Package: surveymerge
Type: Package
Title: Work with Relational Survey Exports and Repeat Groups
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Kasim", "Chambulilo", email = "kassimchambulilo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for working with relational survey exports that contain
    repeat groups and nested repeat groups, as produced by XLSForm-based
    platforms such as ODK Central and KoboToolbox. Helps users inspect
    parent-child sheet relationships, navigate nested repeat structures,
    and assemble analysis-ready datasets at the appropriate unit of analysis
    (household, individual, visit, event, etc.) rather than blindly
    flattening every level into one table.
